</figure>
</p>
</div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>The only guacamole recipe you&#8217;ll need, using ripe avocados, onion, cilantro, lime zest + juice, jalapeño, garlic + tomato. So fresh, so good!</em></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><picture decoding="async" class="wp-image-45896">
<source type="image/webp" srcset="https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_123-760x1140.jpg.webp 760w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_123-500x750.jpg.webp 500w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_123-240x360.jpg.webp 240w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_123-768x1152.jpg.webp 768w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_123-1024x1536.jpg.webp 1024w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_123-1365x2048.jpg.webp 1365w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_123-480x720.jpg.webp 480w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_123-360x540.jpg.webp 360w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_123-720x1080.jpg.webp 720w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_123.jpg.webp 1520w" sizes="(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px"/>
<img decoding="async" width="760" height="1140" src="https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_123-760x1140.jpg" alt="" srcset="https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_123-760x1140.jpg 760w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_123-500x750.jpg 500w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_123-240x360.jpg 240w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_123-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_123-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_123-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_123-480x720.jpg 480w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_123-360x540.jpg 360w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_123-720x1080.jpg 720w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_123.jpg 1520w" sizes="(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px"/>
</picture>
</figure>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-why-i-love-this-perfect-guacamole-recipe">why i love this perfect guacamole recipe</h2>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Crowd-favorite.</strong> Guacamole is a dip that just goes well with anything and everything &#8211; <a href="https://damndelicious.net/2019/04/18/mexican-street-tacos/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">tacos</a>, <a href="https://damndelicious.net/2019/01/28/weeknight-chicken-enchiladas/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">enchiladas</a>, <a href="https://damndelicious.net/2019/05/05/carne-asada/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">carne asada</a>, <a href="https://damndelicious.net/2018/02/26/instant-pot-20-minute-chicken-burrito-bowls/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">burrito bowls</a>, or on its own with tortilla chips, and it&#8217;s a guaranteed crowd hit no matter the occasion.</li>



<li><strong>Uses fresh ingredients.</strong> Skip the store-bought guacamole filled with fillers and preservatives! This homemade version is quick, easy, and uses fresh, high-quality ingredients all around &#8211; avocado, onion, cilantro, lime, jalapeño, garlic and tomato.</li>



<li><strong>Can easily be halved or doubled.</strong> This guacamole recipe is very flexible and forgiving, and can easily be halved, doubled or tripled as needed.</li>



<li><strong>Make ahead of time.</strong> Guacamole is known to brown very quickly, but with our tips and tricks (more on that below), you can make guacamole ahead of time and keep it that vibrant green!</li>
</ul>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><picture loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-45892">
<source type="image/webp" srcset="https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_016-760x1140.jpg.webp 760w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_016-500x750.jpg.webp 500w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_016-240x360.jpg.webp 240w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_016-768x1152.jpg.webp 768w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_016-1024x1536.jpg.webp 1024w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_016-1365x2048.jpg.webp 1365w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_016-480x720.jpg.webp 480w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_016-360x540.jpg.webp 360w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_016-720x1080.jpg.webp 720w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_016.jpg.webp 1520w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px"/>
<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="760" height="1140" src="https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_016-760x1140.jpg" alt="" srcset="https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_016-760x1140.jpg 760w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_016-500x750.jpg 500w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_016-240x360.jpg 240w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_016-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_016-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_016-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_016-480x720.jpg 480w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_016-360x540.jpg 360w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_016-720x1080.jpg 720w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_016.jpg 1520w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px"/>
</picture>
</figure>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-qna block-ingredients"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-key-ingredients-for-guacamole">key ingredients for guacamole</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-avocado">Avocado</h3>



<p>For immediate use, look for avocados that are ripe and soft (giving a little), but also firm.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-onion">Onion</h3>



<p>White onion is generally a favorited choice but this recipe calls for red, offering a slightly sweeter, milder and more colorful option.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-cilantro">Cilantro</h3>



<p>Cilantro is a staple ingredient in guacamole, adding bright and slightly tangy flavors to contrast the rich, high fat content of the avocados.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-lime-zest-and-juice">Lime (zest and juice)</h3>



<p>The lime will add bright, zesty flavors, and will also keep the guacamole a vibrant green (the citric acid in lime slows down the oxidation process that turns guacamole brown).</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-jalapeno">Jalapeño</h3>



<p>The jalapeño pepper will add a spicy kick! The heat level can also be customized to taste &#8211; removing the seeds and membranes of the jalapeño will decrease the heat, pickled jalapeño will add some tang and also reduce the heat, and a serrano pepper (in place of the jalapeño) will add the most heat.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-garlic">Garlic</h3>



<p>A little bit of garlic goes a long way, adding warm, savory notes to balance out the creamy texture of the avocado, tangy lime and bright cilantro. Want to go the extra mile? Add roasted garlic instead!</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-tomato">Tomato</h3>



<p>If using, look for firm Roma tomatoes to avoid a watery guacamole, and always fold them in last to keep them from getting mushy.</p>
</div></div>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><picture loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-47096">
<source type="image/webp" srcset="https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/260330_DD_guacamole_205-760x1140.jpg.webp 760w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/260330_DD_guacamole_205-500x750.jpg.webp 500w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/260330_DD_guacamole_205-240x360.jpg.webp 240w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/260330_DD_guacamole_205-768x1152.jpg.webp 768w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/260330_DD_guacamole_205-1024x1536.jpg.webp 1024w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/260330_DD_guacamole_205-1365x2048.jpg.webp 1365w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/260330_DD_guacamole_205-480x720.jpg.webp 480w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/260330_DD_guacamole_205-360x540.jpg.webp 360w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/260330_DD_guacamole_205-720x1080.jpg.webp 720w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/260330_DD_guacamole_205.jpg.webp 1520w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px"/>
<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="760" height="1140" src="https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/260330_DD_guacamole_205-760x1140.jpg" alt="" srcset="https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/260330_DD_guacamole_205-760x1140.jpg 760w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/260330_DD_guacamole_205-500x750.jpg 500w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/260330_DD_guacamole_205-240x360.jpg 240w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/260330_DD_guacamole_205-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/260330_DD_guacamole_205-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/260330_DD_guacamole_205-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/260330_DD_guacamole_205-480x720.jpg 480w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/260330_DD_guacamole_205-360x540.jpg 360w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/260330_DD_guacamole_205-720x1080.jpg 720w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/260330_DD_guacamole_205.jpg 1520w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px"/>
</picture>
</figure>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-qna block-ingredients"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-how-to-pick-the-best-avocado-for-guacamole">How to pick the best avocado for guacamole</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-"></h3>



<p>Pick avocados with dark black, bumpy, pebbly skin that yields to gentle pressure, feeling firm but giving slightly. If the avocado is too squishy, that is a sign that the avocados are overripe (which is not ideal for guacamole). For later use, look for avocados that are firm and bright green.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-how-to-make-guacamole">How to make guacamole</h2>



<ol class="wp-block-list">
<li>Using a fork, gently mash the avocados, leaving some large chunks &#8211; make it as chunky or as smooth as desired</li>



<li>Fold in onion, cilantro, lime zest + juice, jalapeño and garlic</li>



<li>Season with salt and pepper</li>



<li>Fold in tomatoes until just combined</li>



<li>That&#8217;s it!</li>
</ol>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><picture loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-45897">
<source type="image/webp" srcset="https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_128-760x1140.jpg.webp 760w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_128-500x750.jpg.webp 500w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_128-240x360.jpg.webp 240w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_128-768x1152.jpg.webp 768w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_128-1024x1536.jpg.webp 1024w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_128-1365x2048.jpg.webp 1365w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_128-480x720.jpg.webp 480w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_128-360x540.jpg.webp 360w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_128-720x1080.jpg.webp 720w, https://damndelicious.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/251218_DD_Guacamole_128.jpg.webp 1520w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px"/>
