<li><a href="https://damndelicious.net/2019/03/01/green-chicken-enchiladas/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Green Chicken Enchiladas</a></li>



<li><a href="https://damndelicious.net/2019/08/06/easy-chicken-tacos/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Easy Chicken Tacos</a></li>



